                        des Kelhaimer <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien"><add>burger</add></roleName>
                     </rs> und <rs type="person" ref="pe__stephan_kisling_QGW_II_II_3622">Stephans
                        des Kisling, baid <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">burger</roleName> zu Wienn</rs>.</rs></rs>
